summaries.title: AI Transformation in the Forklift Industry
summaries.description: The global forklift market is projected to surge from $5.4 billion in 2019 to $262.8 billion by 2037, driven by AI integration. By 2025, the market size is expected to reach $59.79 billion at a 3.46% CAGR. North America leads, while Asia Pacific shows the fastest growth.
